overview.en: Taking the blockchain as the core, GTG is a global high-quality blockchain game distribution platform which including: game development and agent, block chain game project incubation, live broadcast of game events, electronic competition event organization, game hardware, etc.
overview.zh: GTG是以区块链为核心的优质区块链游戏分发平台。提供了包括：游戏的开发以及代理、区块链游戏项目孵化、游戏赛事直播、电竞赛事筹办、游戏硬件等。
